# Project Overview

This is a **static landing page** for the Cursor AI code editor, built as a training/demo project.

## Stack

- Plain HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript — no build tools, no frameworks
- [Lucide Icons](https://lucide.dev) loaded via CDN (`unpkg.com/lucide@latest`)
- Google Fonts: **Inter** (UI) and **Fira Code** (monospace)

## Design System

- Dark theme only — base color `#000000`, elevated surfaces `#111111`
- Two accent colors: `--accent-blue: #3b82f6` and `--accent-purple: #8b5cf6`
- All design tokens are CSS custom properties defined in `:root` inside `style.css`
- Glass-morphism panels via the `.glass-panel` utility class

## Sections

1. Navbar (fixed, becomes opaque on scroll)
2. Hero — headline, CTA, editor mockup with typing animation
3. Features grid — 3 cards
4. Testimonial
5. Footer
